================================================================================
STRINGS.XML - TEXT RESOURCES
================================================================================

PURPOSE:
    All user-visible text in the app is defined here.

WHY USE STRING RESOURCES?
    1. Easy translation - just create strings.xml for each language
    2. Consistency - same text used everywhere
    3. Easy updates - change text in one place

NAMING CONVENTION:
    - screen_element_description
    - Example: login_button_sign_in, chat_input_hint

================================================================================
-->
